India: New Delhi is the most polluted city on earth right now
Fresh air doesn't exist in New Delhi at the moment.
Measurements taken at the US Embassy in Delhi put the city's Air Quality Index at 999 on Monday, off the standard chart, which finishes at the "hazardous" level of 500.
BeijingChandrapur Beijing was a pleasant 30, while India's next most polluted city, coal and industry-heavy Chandrapur , recorded levels of 824, according to the World Air Quality Index.